.SH NAME
loop_set_status_from_info \- configure device from loop_info
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" loop_set_status_from_info
.BI "(struct loop_device *lo "  ","
.BI "const struct loop_info64 *info "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "lo" 12
struct loop_device to configure
.IP "info" 12
struct loop_info64 to configure the device with
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Configures the loop device parameters according to the passed
in loop_info64 configuration.
